Devraj Ready, Chairman for the Southern African Coal Processing Society, discusses how the Society is helping drive technology change and improvements in the coal industry. This year marked the 50th anniversary of the SACPS and the organisers pulled out all the stops to ensure that the 2019 conference was bigger, better and more informative than ever before. Read more about coal The prevailing theme at this year’s conference was “Coal Processing – Extracting value from low-grade reserves.”  